### Hadith 3:307

*Narrated Abu Hazim:*

Some men came to Sahl bin Sad to ask him about the pulpit. He replied,
"Allah's Apostle sent for a woman (Sahl named her) (this message):
'Order your slave carpenter to make pieces of wood (i.e. a pulpit) for
me so that I may sit on it while addressing the people.' So, she ordered
him to make it from the tamarisk of the forest. He brought it to her and
she sent it to Allah's Apostle . Allah's Apostle ordered it to be placed
in the mosque: so, it was put and he sat on it.

